{"tid":1989993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post]係咪已經光復左香港啦?","createTime":"2020-04-26T11:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T12:44:21.000Z","uid":129269,"like":13,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"74ef2598e44737756d34080ea8bb81bd65b23b31","tid":1989993,"uid":129269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>求幫推到上熱門</strong></span><br />\nDSE生登記做選民點解無人講<br />\n好多巴絲開左好多post推左好耐都推唔起<br />\n係咪好耐無做野 雖然時間有D急 但<strong>絕對做得切</strong><br />\n聽日DSE通識科 <span style=\"color: red;\">1230</span>放<br />\n約人一齊去<span style=\"color: red;\">派申請表格</span>比DSE生填<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 增加立法會選舉勝算</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#索取表格途徑</span></strong><br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=56dd7673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：<br />\n-&gt; 香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt; 九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n4。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>自己印</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=20300103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#ToDoList</span></strong><br />\n1. 揀番自己會去既區 (揀D唔夠人既區去派)<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe3P1gVsV8qfN5RZp8HgZ4Nza2_qWFfpDsDCxMDcf_vcTTHUg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe3P1gVsV8qfN5RZp8HgZ4Nza2_qWFfpDsDCxMDcf_vcTTHUg%2Fviewform&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=cd2ba6af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe3P1gVsV8qfN5RZp8HgZ4Nza2_qWFfpDsDCxMDcf_vcTTHUg/viewform</a><br />\n2. 將消息send比朋友 令更多人加入行動<br />\n3. 去拎/印表格<br />\n4. 準時到達考試埸地<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#考埸查詢</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Ftc%2FHKDSE%2Fadmin%2Fexam_centres%2Fexam_centres.html&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=b2305fb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#注意事項</span></strong><br />\n1. 係考試完結之後先派發登記表<br />\n2. 唔好打擾考試節奏<br />\n3. 由於有限聚令 大家請留意社交距離 切勿於多於4人情況下派發表格<br />\n4. 7月25日前夠18歲都可以成為選民<br />\n<br />\n考試時間表<br />\n27/4 8:30 - 10:30 通識教育（一）<br />\n27/4 11:15 - 12:30 通識教育（二）<br />\n28/4 8:30 - 10:00 英國語文 （一）<br />\n28/4 11:00 - 13:00 英國語文 （二）<br />\n29/4 9:15 - 12:10 英國語文 （三）（聆聽及綜合能力考核）<br />\n2/5 8:30 - 10:45 數學 必修部分 （一）<br />\n2/5 11:30 - 12:45 數學 必修部分 （二）"},{"pid":"b0363b21e2646c38c7b6c68c7a9d1f3b6d9281c8","tid":1989993,"uid":129269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T11:22:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d200e120166c8db605f3b4c105641431ec1e421e","tid":1989993,"uid":129269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T11:22:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26a1b196c1b98257a25c7853c638caa439569c2e","tid":1989993,"uid":129269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06d5fa276ed45edb713a515b8dbe981937e0e9a7","tid":1989993,"uid":129269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b671f178c0403d8e4bbe24b5f3dd16eb83f73576","tid":1989993,"uid